# Code Owners for codex-plugin-cc
#
# This file declares who is automatically requested for review on PRs that
# touch matching paths. CODEOWNERS only auto-requests humans/teams with
# write access; AI reviewer apps (Claude, Codex Connector, Devin, Copilot)
# are wired separately via their own GitHub App configurations and the
# Copilot ruleset on `main`.
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner — all paths fall back to this.
*                                  @Kenmege

# Workflow + release surfaces — extra-careful review.
.github/                           @Kenmege
.github/workflows/                 @Kenmege

# Security-sensitive surfaces.
SECURITY.md                        @Kenmege
schemas/                           @Kenmege
scripts/bin/git-safe.mjs           @Kenmege
scripts/lib/claude.mjs             @Kenmege

# Release-critical metadata.
package.json                       @Kenmege
package-lock.json                  @Kenmege
.codex-plugin/plugin.json          @Kenmege
CHANGELOG.md                       @Kenmege
